- First District.

E. H. Ashdown, defendant in error, v. The Village of Matteson, plaintiff in error.Gen. No. 35,316.Opinion filed December 28, 1931.Rehearing denied January 11, 1932.W. Otto Wielgoreelci, for plaintiff in error; Walter F. Briody, of counsel. Samuel K. Markman, for defendant in error; Francis L: Brinkman and John P. Sullivan, of counsel. Mr. Presiding Justice O’Connor

delivered the opinion of the court.
